	      <p>Said to be located by K. P. Poonacha by <ref target="bibl:Sarma1993">Varaprasada Rao</ref> in 1993, but it
	      was already known to M. S. Nagaraja Rao in 1985.
	      The find-spot of this stela was <placeName key="pl:Jewargi">Jewargi</placeName>, upstream
	      from Sannati.</p>
